		<title>英国发现四例猴天花</title>
		<link>http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/18/10/4/n10761362.htm</link>
		<pubDate>Thu, 04 Oct 2018 16:30:55 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[各地分网]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[新闻]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[欧洲]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[社会新闻]]></category>
