		<title>法国明年减税60亿 80％家庭逐步减少住房税</title>
		<link>http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/18/10/3/n10758112.htm</link>
		<pubDate>Wed, 03 Oct 2018 21:24:30 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[各地分网]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[大图新闻]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[新闻]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[欧洲]]></category>
