		<title>麦德龙出售Real超市  美国亚马逊或出手</title>
		<link>http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/18/9/25/n10739571.htm</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 25 Sep 2018 09:04:44 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[各地分网]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[德国]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[德国新闻]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[新闻资讯]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[欧洲]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[麦德龙]]></category>
