		<title>破梅西C罗十年垄断 莫德里奇获足球先生</title>
		<link>http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/18/9/25/n10738647.htm</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 25 Sep 2018 00:30:31 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[各地分网]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[国际足球]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[新闻]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[欧洲]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[英伦生活网]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[体育新闻]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[体育要闻]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[足球先生]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[莫德里奇]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[梅西]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[C罗]]></category>
